<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0">

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-9ndCyUaIbzAi2FUVXJi0CjmCapSmO7SnpJef0486qhLnuZ2cdeRhO02iuK6FUUVM" crossorigin="anonymous">


    <style>
        body{
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;

            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
    
    <div style="width: 100%; height: 100%;  text-align: center;">
        <div style="height: 35px; width: 100%; margin-top: 7px;">
            <img src="/img_back" alt="no img;" onclick="history.back()" style="width: 25px; height: 25px; float: left; margin-left: 8px;">
        </div>

        <div style="height: 25px; width: 100%; background-color: #EDEDED; line-height: 25px;">TREASURE HUNT</div>
        
        <div style="width: 90%; margin-left: 5%; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; ">발견한 쪽지의 코드를 입력해 주세요</div>
        

        <form action="/treasure_answer" method="get" style="width: 90%; margin-left: 5%;">
            <label style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 3px;">학번:</label>
            <input type="text" id="quiz_year" name="quiz_year" style="width: 30px; height: 25px; font-size: 15px; margin-right: 10px;">
            <label style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 3px; margin-right: 5px;">이름:</label>
            <input type="text" id="quiz_name" name="quiz_name" style="width: 70px; height: 25px; font-size: 15px;">
            

            <div style="width: 250px; margin: 0 auto; margin-top: 50px;">
                <input type="text" id="treasure_code" name="treasure_code" class="form-control" placeholder="Code" style="width: 120px; height: 30px; float: left;">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mb-3" style="width: 105px; height: 30px; font-weight: bold; padding: 0;">달란트 받기</button>
            </div>
        </form>

        <div style="width: 100%; height: 20px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 15px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; color: crimson;">
            "달란트 받기"를 누르고 3초간 기다려주세요!
        </div>

        <div style="width: 86%; height: 20px; margin-left: 7%; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; text-align: left; color: crimson;">
            코드를 입력했는데도 달란드가 적립되지 않는다면 회장단에게 문의해 주세요.
        </div>

        



        

    </div>



</body>
</html>